{"type":null,"faqId":49899,"title":"在其他非杂志锁屏主题下如何实现微信、QQ和短信显示消息悬浮弹框提示的功能？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body27155410\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022307192__p62582666\">您好，具体操作步骤如下：</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022307192__p26373084\">首先，设置您想要的主题：打开桌面的主题应用 &gt; 我的，在该栏目下面选择您想要的主题，如星火主题；</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022307192__p36031167\">再次在桌面上打开设置 &gt; 锁屏和密码 &gt; 锁屏样式  &gt; 选默认（杂志锁屏） &gt; 点击应用，即可实现杂志锁屏样式。</p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022307192","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448627796000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":26,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"非杂志锁屏,主题,微信,QQ,短信,显示消息,悬浮弹框提示","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}